Hi,
  Abstract class handle allows construction to an object, see below code. Is this check not implemented in Icarus yet?

Thanks
Srini

```verilog
package test_pkg;

  virtual class ivl_uvm_base_test;
    function new ();
    endfunction : new 

    virtual task run_phase ();
      $display ("%m run_phase");
    endtask : run_phase 
  endclass : ivl_uvm_base_test

  task run_test ();
    ivl_uvm_base_test u_t_0;

    u_t_0 = new();
    u_t_0.run_phase ();
  endtask : run_test 
endpackage : test_pkg

module m;
  import test_pkg::*;

  initial begin
    run_test ();
  end
endmodule : m


```

